Let’s congratulate 🎉Black Girls Who Rock St. Louis Honoree Award Winning Journalist April Simpson, Anchor @wishtv8 . We hope to see everyone at the Red Carpet Celebration Sunday  December 10 ,2023  at @lindenwooduniversity J. Scheidegger Center For The Arts. We will honor  100 women in the community. The event is hosted by the National Council of Negro Women Inc., St. Louis Section, Divine Daughters and The R. Whittington Foundation. A portion of the proceeds will go towards adopting 100 families for Christmas 🎄 Get your tickets !#blackgirlswhorockstl #EpicEvents
